{"tid":2062031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發提堂！！緊急聲援！！6月13號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-06-13T00:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T03:15:49.000Z","uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8d46add724c6126bb827fddee754b9752f95fea7","tid":2062031,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:22:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">🛑🛑🛑突發提堂🛑🛑🛑緊急聲援🛑🛑🛑</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n🏛觀 塘 裁 判 法 院 3 樓 1 庭<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️徐綺薇署理主任裁判官<br />\n🕤09:30<br />\n👤 盧男(23)<br />\n#新案件 #20200611西貢 管有爆炸品）"},{"pid":"747d3f1caafaf208f1c6e6331af3e85e0a9159ec","tid":2062031,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:22:10.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=f8bb6b87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"161994e8938afa10f8d83c73d8582c61cbf0d44d","tid":2062031,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:22:20.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=045f8dc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=752b46a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"560c80970212e258a3ac2c7436ccd8d10872bb28","tid":2062031,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdRTuW7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdRTuW7.jpg&h=d63e40a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"174ab5b1ceb7fc60c2a97d936c85c898e26e0554","tid":2062031,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測<br />\n</strong>- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"92297cc99598fdcefe076f7fd590434f43043043","tid":2062031,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:23:11.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n觀塘裁判法院交通<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界</strong><br />\n上水：<br />\n277E                        [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n粉嶺：<br />\n277X                        [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n大埔：<br />\n74X 到大老山<br />\n轉乘 89D, 277E/X   [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n馬鞍山：<br />\n89D                          [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n沙田：<br />\n89/B/C/X 到大老山<br />\n轉乘 89D, 277E/X  [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n將軍澳：<br />\n296A                       [觀塘法院]<br />\n坑口、寶林：<br />\n98A                         [觀塘法院]<br />\n青衣、荃灣：<br />\n42C                         [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n葵芳：<br />\n38                           [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n屯門：<br />\n258D, 259D            [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n油塘：<br />\n14B                         [觀塘法院]<br />\n藍田：<br />\n14B, 15A                [觀塘法院]<br />\n慈雲山：<br />\n15A                         [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n黃大仙：<br />\n14, 15, 38, 42C, 258D, 259D   [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n九龍灣：<br />\n14/B, 15/A, 16, 38, 42C, 89D [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n土瓜灣：<br />\n14, 15                     [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n尖沙咀：<br />\n14X, 215X             [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n旺角：<br />\n16, 93K, 296C       [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n深水埗：<br />\n296C                      [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中環、灣仔：<br />\n619, 641⚠️注意服務時間 [觀塘法院]<br />\n灣仔：<br />\n601, 619, 641            [觀塘法院]<br />\n銅鑼灣：<br />\n601, 619, 671(建議) [觀塘法院]<br />\n東區：<br />\n606                        [觀塘法院]<br />\n鴨脷洲、黃竹坑：<br />\n671                        [觀塘法院]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"00a61fceba75b41dff661394f0b0a715555af25f","tid":2062031,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:23:39.000Z","msg":"【保釋及送車位置】<br />\n<br />\n✵送車位位於法院停車場🅿️<br />\n✵揾唔到就圍住法院兜一圈⭕️<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《觀 塘 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左再轉左（馬路燈前轉）／正門轉右再轉右（見到郵政局轉）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>特別鳴謝被捕人士關注組公海手足cc整合以上資訊</strong>"},{"pid":"5f561dcda8528ea7f6c446786214d744fc88bdda","tid":2062031,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"法庭聲援要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />突發提堂！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gi